\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking (safety)
MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking == []([][ParticipantVoiceState = Muted => ~is_speaking]_ParticipantVoiceState)

\* Property: RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants (safety)
RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants == []([][participant_count <= max_participants]_participant_count)

\* Property: NegotiationEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
NegotiationEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(PeerNegotiation = Connected))

